column2: SELECT       a.name, a.radeg AS radeg, a.decdeg AS radeg, p.objID, p.ra, p.dec,       p.cModelMag_u, p.cModelMag_g, p.cModelMag_r, p.cModelMag_i, p.cModelMag_z,       p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z,       p.petroMag_u, p.petroMag_r, p.petroR5#_r, p.petroR9#_r,       p.expRad_u, p.expRad_g, p.expRad_r, p.expRad_i,       p.expAB_u, p.expAB_g, p.expAB_r, p.expAB_i,       p.fracDeV_u, p.fracDeV_g, p.fracDeV_r, p.fracDeV_i,       p.extinction_u, p.extinction_g, p.extinction_r, p.extinction_i,       p.lnLDeV_r, p.type, p.specObjID into mydb.New_Table_# from mydb.MyTable_# AS a       CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( radeg, decdeg, #) AS n        JOIN PhotoPrimary AS p ON n.objid=p.objid
